"{\"uid\": \"forbes.com-sites-jaymcgregor-2024-07-26-samsung-galaxy-fold-6-flip-6-olympics-discount-galaxy-s24-ultra\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByJanhoi McGregor,  Senior Contributor.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 39, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX_facilities\", \"score\": 0.9958107713975387, \"rank\": 0.004194304605647663, \"text\": \"McGregor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX_facilities\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SpaceX_facilities\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung'shigh trade-in prices have finished.\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 85, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the discount are not, because the company has immediately followed up that deal with another another Galaxy Z Fold 6 promotion.\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To mark the start of the Oympics, from July 26th to August 13th, Samsung will give \\u00a3150 ($192.94) cashback on purchases of select phones in the U.K. That cashback offer can rise to \\u00a3300 ($385.88) for one in three shoppers via a scratch card competition.\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997918307816, \"rank\": 2.0401785017314265e-07, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, anyone who buys one of the phones listed below from Samsung's U.K. website will get a guaranteed \\u00a3150 discount.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997918307816, \"rank\": 2.0401785017314265e-07, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will have to do a bit of work to get your money back, though.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A cashback claim must be submitted within 30 days via the online claim form with the same information that the phone was bought with.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The big pre-order deals are over, however.Samsung is not offering its free storage upgrade from 256GB to 512GB, nor is it still offering high trade-in prices for your old phone, or Samsung Care + for free.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this, \\u00a3150 off the headline price is still a solid deal andmatches the company's last Galaxy S24 sale earlier this month,which came just a few days before Galaxy Unpacked.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1169, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galaxy_Unpacked\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Galaxy Unpacked\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galaxy_Unpacked\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Galaxy_Unpacked\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What is missing are enhanced trade-in prices, which is where real savings are made.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have an old phone, it may be worth holding on to it for the next sale that combines straight money off a new handset, and enhanced trade-in values.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a look at how much Samsung wasoffering for five year old phones just a few days ago.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What we can be sure of is that Samsung will likely giveaway double storage, free Samsung Care+ and other types of discounts again in the near future.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company has repeatedly slashed the price its Galaxy S24 since it launched in January,as has Google with its Pixel 8.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9995527012657401, \"rank\": 0.0004474983083628092, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both companies have been locked in a price war for the last seven months and with Google's upcoming Pixel 9 launch, followed by Apple's iPhone 16 in September, Samsung will almost certainly respond with a new deal.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9995527012657401, \"rank\": 0.0004474983083628092, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Pixel\", \"score\": 0.9999638002690778, \"rank\": 3.6201041407478914e-05, \"text\": \"Pixel\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Pixel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Pixel\"}, {\"begin\": 1916, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999934062, \"rank\": 6.536274195388309e-12, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.998032847417544, \"rank\": 0.001971029893191883, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}]}"